---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Complete Guide to Online Store Marketing in Canada | Lead Flow North">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/ecommerce-retail/online-stores" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Online Stores
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">E-Commerce</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">14 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          The Complete Guide to Online Store Marketing Automation
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
          Recover abandoned carts, drive repeat purchases, and reduce ad dependency with automated email and SMS.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 to-teal-600 rounded-2xl h-64 md:h-96 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center text-white">
            <div class="text-6xl mb-4">ðŸ›’</div>
            <div class="text-xl font-semibold">E-Commerce Marketing Automation</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          
          <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
            E-commerce success isn't just about trafficâ€”it's about conversion and retention. The stores that win are those that automate the customer journey from first visit to repeat purchase.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl my-8">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4 mt-0">What You'll Learn</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mb-0">
              <li><a href="#cart" class="text-emerald-600 hover:underline">Abandoned Cart Recovery</a></li>
              <li><a href="#post-purchase" class="text-emerald-600 hover:underline">Post-Purchase Sequences</a></li>
              <li><a href="#winback" class="text-emerald-600 hover:underline">Customer Win-Back</a></li>
              <li><a href="#reviews" class="text-emerald-600 hover:underline">Product Review Generation</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <h2 id="cart" class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Abandoned Cart Recovery</h2>

          <p>
            About 70% of online shopping carts are abandoned. That's revenue sitting on the table. A well-crafted recovery sequence can bring back 10-30% of those abandoners.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">The Perfect Cart Recovery Sequence</h3>

          <div class="bg-emerald-50 p-6 rounded-xl my-6">
            <ol class="space-y-3 mb-0">
              <li><strong>1 hour:</strong> "Forget something?" reminder with cart contents</li>
              <li><strong>24 hours:</strong> "Still thinking?" with social proof</li>
              <li><strong>48 hours:</strong> Small incentive (free shipping, 10% off)</li>
              <li><strong>72 hours:</strong> Final reminder with urgency</li>
            </ol>
          </div>

          <h2 id="post-purchase" class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Post-Purchase Sequences</h2>

          <p>
            The period after purchase is critical for building loyalty. Order updates build trust, and timed recommendations drive repeat purchases.
          </p>

          <h2 id="winback" class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Customer Win-Back</h2>

          <p>
            Customers who haven't purchased in 60-90 days are at risk of churning. Win-back campaigns re-engage them before they forget you.
          </p>

          <h2 id="reviews" class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Product Review Generation</h2>

          <p>
            Products with reviews convert dramatically better. Request reviews at the right timeâ€”after delivery when excitement is high.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 to-teal-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Grow Your Store?</h3>
            <p class="text-emerald-100 mb-6">
              Get a free consultation and see exactly how we'd implement these automations for your online store.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 text-emerald-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
